        "timestamp": "2022-12-13 02:12:50.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI run tox manually, and I get the following error\nAttributeError: module 'collections' has no attribute 'Callable'\nGoogling gives me https://github.com/rbarrois/xworkflows/issues/16",
        "patchset_number": 2
